/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>ABB董事长认为红海扰乱的影响有限</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/abb-chairman-sees-limited-impact-red-sea-disruptions-2024-01-15/</link><description>瑞士工程集团 ABB 董事长 Peter Voser 周一在达沃斯世界经济论坛 (WEF) 年会之前接受采访时表示，红海中断对其供应链的影响有限。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 20:24:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/abb-chairman-sees-limited-impact-red-sea-disruptions-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>阿斯利康表示，到目前为止，红海中断并未造成供应中断</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/astrazeneca-says-no-supply-snags-so-far-red-sea-disruptions-2024-01-15/</link><description>制药商阿斯利康（AstraZeneca）周一在世界经济论坛（WEF）前夕向路透社表示，到目前为止，尚未发现因红海运输中断而出现任何供应问题。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 17:37:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/astrazeneca-says-no-supply-snags-so-far-red-sea-disruptions-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>瑞士应泽连斯基要求主办乌克兰和平峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraines-zelenskiy-wants-china-join-global-peace-summit-2024-01-15/</link><description>应乌克兰总统泽伦斯基的要求，瑞士周一同意主办乌克兰问题全球和平峰会。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 17:12:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraines-zelenskiy-wants-china-join-global-peace-summit-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>2024 年的预期：美联储转向、通胀降温、增长放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/what-expect-2024-fed-pivot-cooling-inflation-easing-growth-2024-01-15/</link><description>大型银行表示，今年全球经济增长可能会放缓，但美联储立场的鸽派倾斜提高了人们对美国经济的希望，并提振了风险资产的前景。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 16:07:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/what-expect-2024-fed-pivot-cooling-inflation-easing-growth-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>2024 年达沃斯：Bajaj Finserv 首席执行官表示，印度正处于 FDI 洪流的风口浪尖</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-cusp-fdi-flood-bajaj-finserv-chair-says-davos-2024-01-15/</link><description>作者：A Galani 和 Anthony Slodkowski</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 14:45:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-cusp-fdi-flood-bajaj-finserv-chair-says-davos-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>格鲁吉亚执政党领导人访华推动深化双边关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/georgias-ruling-party-leader-visits-china-push-deeper-ties-2024-01-15/</link><description>据格鲁吉亚媒体报道，格鲁吉亚执政党领导人周一开始对中国进行为期六天的访问，这个欧盟候选成员国寻求深化与北京的关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 14:36:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/georgias-ruling-party-leader-visits-china-push-deeper-ties-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>玩具制造商从中国转移并非易事</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/toy-manufacturers-shift-china-is-no-childs-play-2024-01-15/</link><description>正在努力应对中国成本飙升的玩具制造商在将生产转移到更便宜的地方时没有找到简单的选择。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 13:09:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/toy-manufacturers-shift-china-is-no-childs-play-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国与瑞士签署扩大贸易宣言</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-switzerland-sign-declaration-with-view-expanding-trade-2024-01-15/</link><description>瑞士政府表示，李强总理会见瑞士总统后，中国和瑞士周一签署了一份联合声明，同意深化合作伙伴关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 13:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-switzerland-sign-declaration-with-view-expanding-trade-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>危地马拉自由派新领导人反腐面临巨大障碍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/reformist-arevalo-assumes-guatemalan-presidency-after-opposition-delays-2024-01-15/</link><description>危地马拉新任自由派总统贝尔纳多·阿雷瓦洛(Bernardo Arevalo)在长期拖延后于周一早些时候上任，这突显了他在满足高期望和在反对派控制的国会中制定全面反腐败议程方面面临着艰巨的斗争。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 12:35:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/reformist-arevalo-assumes-guatemalan-presidency-after-opposition-delays-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>解释者：胡塞武装袭击暴露了中国在红海的商业利益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/houthi-attacks-expose-chinas-commercial-stakes-red-sea-2024-01-15/</link><description>中国呼吁停止对红海民用船只的袭击，这种袭击极大地扩大了哈马斯与以色列的冲突，并使北京在苏伊士运河沿岸的商业利益面临风险。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 12:20:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/houthi-attacks-expose-chinas-commercial-stakes-red-sea-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜黑客与犯罪分子在东南亚共享洗钱网络 - 联合国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korean-hackers-criminals-share-money-laundering-networks-southeast-asia-un-2024-01-15/</link><description>根据周一发布的联合国报告，朝鲜黑客正在与东南亚的欺诈者和毒贩共享洗钱和地下银行网络，赌场和加密货币交易所成为有组织犯罪的主要场所。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 12:00:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korean-hackers-criminals-share-money-laundering-networks-southeast-asia-un-2024-01-15/</guid></item></channel></rss>